{"title":"03-Sindromes-Geriatricos-Domicilio","guid":"","filepath":"/Users/criaah/Vault/📚 Resources/Mapas-Mentales/Apuntes-de-Clases/MUE-USS/MUE_Emergencias_Diabeticas.smmx","root":{"id":"0","parent":"-1","text":"EMERGENCIAS DIABETICAS EN URGENCIA","guid":"LVtKU9ziTUS-BhC7IC-PKw","children":[{"id":"1","parent":"0","text":"CETOACIDOSIS DIABETICA (CAD)","guid":"VhYcUJXBTSKQBdPjkPT7Dg","children":[{"id":"2","parent":"1","text":"Definicion","guid":"nMiWkJVtS-W6ey6Z9tNcZA","children":[{"id":"3","parent":"2","text":"Hiperglicemia + acidosis metabolica + cetonemia","guid":"QfmLPEwWToGSffocU1A7Uw","children":[]},{"id":"4","parent":"2","text":"Triada: glicemia >250 mg/dL + pH <7.3 + cetonas (+)","guid":"b1i7lyc-QqK5gnochZ28Eg","children":[]},{"id":"5","parent":"2","text":"Brecha anionica elevada (>12 mEq/L)","guid":"DA7zzgtwR4CtHH_BjnNwVA","children":[]}]},{"id":"6","parent":"1","text":"Clasificacion de gravedad (ADA)","guid":"uk2hqVhRS9aecDLoRQXw8g","children":[{"id":"7","parent":"6","text":"LEVE → pH 7.25-7.30, HCO3 15-18, alerta","guid":"TdFi1XlkTzGyHUBQOo46Bw","children":[]},{"id":"8","parent":"6","text":"MODERADA → pH 7.0-7.24, HCO3 10-14, somnoliento","guid":"NLAwIOZVQuKvAf14voFzDw","children":[]},{"id":"9","parent":"6","text":"SEVERA → pH <7.0, HCO3 <10, estupor/coma","guid":"65jafnowSQ6pcB3oIWAMGA","children":[]}]},{"id":"10","parent":"1","text":"Fisiopatologia","guid":"_OJ3CfkjRJCsPXiPCrmuJQ","children":[{"id":"11","parent":"10","text":"Deficit absoluto o relativo de insulina","guid":"JsfVgDk_SbSEAIvdifanvA","children":[]},{"id":"12","parent":"10","text":"Hormonas contrarreguladoras ↑ (glucagon, cortisol, GH, catecolaminas)","guid":"iPKn4eR3TC6gH_n56IPHaQ","children":[]},{"id":"13","parent":"10","text":"Lipólisis → AGL → cetogenesis hepatica","guid":"s33GDMxZQCCaG_O46lGx-A","children":[{"id":"14","parent":"13","text":"Acetoacetato, beta-hidroxibutirato, acetona","guid":"gV-AiGKDT3yuMPglcvViTQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"15","parent":"10","text":"Gluconeogenesis y glucogenolisis ↑","guid":"44i4ciB7SzKDJ75cr99O-g","children":[]},{"id":"16","parent":"10","text":"Diuresis osmotica → deshidratacion severa","guid":"nKM0CSepTneYYGi-4v0jWg","children":[]},{"id":"17","parent":"10","text":"Deficit hidrico promedio 5-7 L","guid":"u80kr1SpQMu6gb6XyFKznQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"18","parent":"1","text":"Epidemiologia en adulto mayor","guid":"oL5ezd79RomsEl5JqpNkhg","children":[{"id":"19","parent":"18","text":"CAD en DM2 → 34% de casos (no solo DM1)","guid":"fJm_4542TCmWsgiDgd2NMg","children":[]},{"id":"20","parent":"18","text":"Mayor mortalidad en >65 anos → 50% de muertes por CAD","guid":"7uCUjN60RDOY3wf5FWxHpw","children":[]},{"id":"21","parent":"18","text":"Infeccion como precipitante mas comun en AM","guid":"V6sDCcuVQTebKfP1sI1wOQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"22","parent":"1","text":"Desencadenantes (5 I)","guid":"lXjSvwcLRSWl4Eyx06_z2A","children":[{"id":"23","parent":"22","text":"Infeccion (30-40%) → neumonia, ITU, sepsis","guid":"RM3lJ934Tj-hJQ2-Oui3GA","children":[]},{"id":"24","parent":"22","text":"Incumplimiento tratamiento insulinico","guid":"UaSsiYWqSvC41nSNnbCyQw","children":[]},{"id":"25","parent":"22","text":"Infarto (IAM, ACV)","guid":"FfdGFdMwRxi6pHBkVUwHbQ","children":[]},{"id":"26","parent":"22","text":"Inicio de diabetes (debut)","guid":"8tem8ClcRJGbfYOkbG-L8A","children":[]},{"id":"27","parent":"22","text":"Ingesta de farmacos → corticoides, iSGLT2","guid":"dWoeBoY0TrGOoFq3pBAQsw","children":[{"id":"28","parent":"27","text":"PERLA → CAD euglucemica por iSGLT2","guid":"dQ2kYDMxQJmCpHANRAmu5g","children":[]},{"id":"29","parent":"27","text":"Glicemia normal o levemente elevada","guid":"jMnujOBsS5WRZaP_ZuRiGw","children":[]},{"id":"30","parent":"27","text":"Alta sospecha si iSGLT2 + acidosis + cetonas","guid":"60VrbxZoSeW7TE4fJ3MLhw","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"31","parent":"1","text":"Presentacion clinica","guid":"Rugo-uTYRHeK7Cg1zWW_lA","children":[{"id":"32","parent":"31","text":"Poliuria, polidipsia, perdida peso","guid":"xPT6r0NYQ6mY1jqtzyVjeQ","children":[]},{"id":"33","parent":"31","text":"Nauseas, vomitos, dolor abdominal","guid":"fza2R77TQsqzao4NXEEW_w","children":[]},{"id":"34","parent":"31","text":"Respiracion de Kussmaul (rapida, profunda)","guid":"BHFT6thFQfS3EaZftYXhyw","children":[]},{"id":"35","parent":"31","text":"Aliento cetonico (frutal)","guid":"1sRzREOORqub91r4J6Ausg","children":[]},{"id":"36","parent":"31","text":"Deshidratacion, taquicardia, hipotension","guid":"IUoMJcr1Q6erkBw8NJKDmw","children":[]},{"id":"37","parent":"31","text":"EN ADULTO MAYOR","guid":"MADw3VFKT1SpJNnO26j1uA","children":[{"id":"38","parent":"37","text":"Sintomas menos clasicos","guid":"rUSiY6C1RQW0aofQP0ptug","children":[]},{"id":"39","parent":"37","text":"Confusion/delirium como presentacion principal","guid":"trM1MJ9lS3W9eWexiKqsaw","children":[]},{"id":"40","parent":"37","text":"Dolor abdominal puede simular abdomen agudo","guid":"9AJtSX3LR4GVXh_J3XB3kw","children":[]},{"id":"41","parent":"37","text":"Kussmaul puede estar ausente si debilidad muscular","guid":"vOLQud_DRw62Q6tOVCehzw","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"42","parent":"1","text":"Laboratorio","guid":"I7vR-tBiRyqFNC8kGm2kXw","children":[{"id":"43","parent":"42","text":"Glicemia → generalmente >250 mg/dL","guid":"XzDT1XwASDqVDcl3bY4RGQ","children":[]},{"id":"44","parent":"42","text":"Gases arteriales → pH, HCO3, pCO2","guid":"2K6k2I8OQ3-RYfQ0pcMG4A","children":[]},{"id":"45","parent":"42","text":"Cetonas → beta-hidroxibutirato (preferido) o cetonuria","guid":"-P2U6s6ESoKbVkiIjYIcZw","children":[]},{"id":"46","parent":"42","text":"Electrolitos → Na, K, Cl, brecha anionica","guid":"d2W3qlbIRPGRF-dwg0GX7A","children":[]},{"id":"47","parent":"42","text":"SODIO CORREGIDO → Na + 1.6 por cada 100 mg/dL de glicemia >100","guid":"JKm9Ack0Q4ClppkvyDdNTg","children":[]},{"id":"48","parent":"42","text":"POTASIO → puede estar normal/alto pese a deficit corporal total","guid":"xJvoVoztQe-O6fudv0Dw0w","children":[{"id":"49","parent":"48","text":"K <3.5 → reponer ANTES de insulina","guid":"xQEWjUt2RQK6S9iw6XpZ8Q","children":[]},{"id":"50","parent":"48","text":"K 3.5-5.3 → reponer con fluidos","guid":"G85X7dQVRcWkSuBVm0O9hQ","children":[]},{"id":"51","parent":"48","text":"K >5.3 → no reponer, monitorizar","guid":"bIuHhYVPQG-ifrZj74kglQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"52","parent":"42","text":"BUN, creatinina, osmolaridad","guid":"_asq79heSBuHSBiDUMNfEA","children":[]},{"id":"53","parent":"42","text":"Hemograma, PCR, lactato","guid":"2mv7f-95TxiScqNEZS0n-Q","children":[]},{"id":"54","parent":"42","text":"ECG (descartar IAM como precipitante)","guid":"E8StfsteQS6cOwWr8qwtOg","children":[]},{"id":"55","parent":"42","text":"Rx torax si sospecha neumonia","guid":"Rhudx2DXTI-zbKHXJrHT7A","children":[]}]},{"id":"56","parent":"1","text":"Manejo","guid":"FskZWwUnTSO6cfXn14xAjQ","children":[{"id":"57","parent":"56","text":"FLUIDOS → prioridad #1","guid":"qFO8nzf6QVal9R1dEZDkmg","children":[{"id":"58","parent":"57","text":"SF 0.9% → 1-1.5 L primera hora","guid":"XVYflGOtS6-DX5wfSHCqWQ","children":[]},{"id":"59","parent":"57","text":"Luego 250-500 mL/h segun estado hidratacion","guid":"c6712bIGQa21CMcex_XpLQ","children":[]},{"id":"60","parent":"57","text":"Cambiar a SF 0.45% si Na corregido >145","guid":"JsP9Ga-wT1aU6qytGLZOeg","children":[]},{"id":"61","parent":"57","text":"Agregar SG 5% cuando glicemia <250","guid":"bYff4K9yQwO5D8_twxRZcA","children":[]},{"id":"62","parent":"57","text":"EN ADULTO MAYOR → velocidad reducida","guid":"qMoGRxoMQgmYVR6C-BgJAA","children":[{"id":"63","parent":"62","text":"Riesgo de edema pulmonar","guid":"Dp9kPG9vTS6AzRSfqOSYpw","children":[]},{"id":"64","parent":"62","text":"Monitorizar PVC o ecocardio si duda","guid":"KLPwytscSMevN6gDRxMd8Q","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"65","parent":"56","text":"INSULINA","guid":"5tAoc3ZCQH-UhiNDBGwYfg","children":[{"id":"66","parent":"65","text":"Bolo 0.1 U/kg IV (opcional, no obligatorio)","guid":"Ww1tSTGuSAqnBnG8j0Jnug","children":[]},{"id":"67","parent":"65","text":"Infusion 0.1 U/kg/h (o 0.14 U/kg/h sin bolo)","guid":"kVaToK7qQJWx_kEC1kwY_Q","children":[]},{"id":"68","parent":"65","text":"Meta → descenso glicemia 50-75 mg/dL/h","guid":"nrQE4IhVTrGaGT9O5yNxPw","children":[]},{"id":"69","parent":"65","text":"Cuando glicemia <250 → reducir a 0.02-0.05 U/kg/h","guid":"FqjGjsV1T9-gvqi0ZmirIw","children":[]},{"id":"70","parent":"65","text":"Agregar SG 5% para mantener glicemia 150-200","guid":"g7xkOawIRvOEG2LbdIwtPA","children":[]},{"id":"71","parent":"65","text":"NO suspender infusion hasta resolver cetoacidosis","guid":"a8mYqR0YTj24BlGE2skHqQ","children":[]},{"id":"72","parent":"65","text":"PERLA → NO iniciar insulina si K <3.5","guid":"A5iMLRRxTUGlUvR-sln4CQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"73","parent":"56","text":"POTASIO","guid":"KpGAXiCeS5eT2_l0iRy-lQ","children":[{"id":"74","parent":"73","text":"Deficit corporal total 3-5 mEq/kg","guid":"NG13YMruS7GMeqnEkXOkzw","children":[]},{"id":"75","parent":"73","text":"K <3.5 → 20-40 mEq/h (retrasar insulina)","guid":"j71StHo-R-iWB-tOtlxvsw","children":[]},{"id":"76","parent":"73","text":"K 3.5-5.3 → 20-30 mEq/L en fluidos","guid":"-dVAk68ZS7edNm1aEMwaBA","children":[]},{"id":"77","parent":"73","text":"K >5.3 → no agregar, medir cada 2h","guid":"4HbPbqkNQQyHepA6KuZ_1w","children":[]}]},{"id":"78","parent":"56","text":"BICARBONATO","guid":"Wmuj9tn9R-Km1b1rX1HncQ","children":[{"id":"79","parent":"78","text":"SOLO si pH <6.9 (controversia en pH 6.9-7.0)","guid":"6RfY7rvNS_yU7PADtdEUuA","children":[]},{"id":"80","parent":"78","text":"NaHCO3 100 mEq en 400 mL + 20 mEq KCl en 2h","guid":"a2lY66Y8TgyiH6LYi0UeWg","children":[]},{"id":"81","parent":"78","text":"No indicado rutinariamente","guid":"U7O21I_rTWa0teV0I61hCw","children":[]}]},{"id":"82","parent":"56","text":"FOSFATO","guid":"uDtjSY5wQ1C9TC4AlidYsQ","children":[{"id":"83","parent":"82","text":"Reponer si <1.0 mg/dL","guid":"6WmKS1KYRgemjIR3SMtddA","children":[]},{"id":"84","parent":"82","text":"O si disfuncion cardiaca/debilidad muscular","guid":"1NJlSPFFQv-oCUYORtdF_A","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"85","parent":"1","text":"Criterios de resolucion","guid":"0UJgk7cYTC6wj_-5lKh7xQ","children":[{"id":"86","parent":"85","text":"Glicemia <200 + al menos 2 de:","guid":"y4r0cncgQ_uHxide_YeUQA","children":[{"id":"87","parent":"86","text":"pH >7.3","guid":"54eWtfabRJyhAWJ3mSwRyw","children":[]},{"id":"88","parent":"86","text":"HCO3 ≥15","guid":"G5fr5mgiTjmWU6Tqor98qQ","children":[]},{"id":"89","parent":"86","text":"Brecha anionica ≤12","guid":"AJi3YzbgQpGmZiKJ2fFrfQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"90","parent":"85","text":"Transicion a insulina SC → solapar 1-2h con infusion IV","guid":"ONXB1RLWTxahF2ZVbEwJvw","children":[]}]},{"id":"91","parent":"1","text":"Complicaciones del tratamiento","guid":"HC9gXMTcTPWIPB9ZZ7oWtg","children":[{"id":"92","parent":"91","text":"Hipoglicemia (si insulina excesiva)","guid":"qJb11MfHROiHhwJuquDYBA","children":[]},{"id":"93","parent":"91","text":"Hipokalemia (si no reposicion adecuada)","guid":"b4cj-jY6TL6jjQxmP9U0RA","children":[]},{"id":"94","parent":"91","text":"Edema cerebral (raro en adultos)","guid":"rbpvz-8dQRW4nzdL0IAo9w","children":[]},{"id":"95","parent":"91","text":"Sobrecarga hidrica (riesgo en AM con IC)","guid":"ZxBBG0WATZSw4ByR7w3-qw","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"96","parent":"0","text":"ESTADO HIPEROSMOLAR HIPERGLICEMICO (EHH)","guid":"dtzhf29tRNWu97CEpOd2RQ","children":[{"id":"97","parent":"96","text":"Definicion","guid":"Ox-MnYXfSIig8wOhwrxUkQ","children":[{"id":"98","parent":"97","text":"Hiperglicemia severa + hiperosmolaridad + deshidratacion","guid":"vFyoq8OeSzSNUZ4FAx2dbg","children":[]},{"id":"99","parent":"97","text":"SIN cetoacidosis significativa","guid":"ikiqkBAgTRqt4vFT9sNvfA","children":[]},{"id":"100","parent":"97","text":"Guia JBDS 2023 (Mustafa, PMID:36370077)","guid":"93Upmc0FRNC8sZ7r0-sY9A","children":[]}]},{"id":"101","parent":"96","text":"Criterios diagnosticos","guid":"EFgsZFm9Ru6nQlKGu9I7zg","children":[{"id":"102","parent":"101","text":"Glicemia >600 mg/dL","gu