]},{"id":"239","parent":"236","text":"Mixto → acidosis + hiperosmolaridad","guid":"eMa-oFoXRAqRqaYl3xibAg","children":[]}]},{"id":"240","parent":"234","text":"En adulto mayor → EHH es MAS frecuente que CAD pura","guid":"aSU1uAYZSkS-Kr7n320w-g","children":[]}]},{"id":"241","parent":"0","text":"CONSIDERACIONES GERIATRICAS TRANSVERSALES","guid":"NFpT93H5SsSWfuVmzsdLyQ","children":[{"id":"242","parent":"241","text":"Metas glicemicas individualizadas","guid":"rFkVjpqdTk-9-5AEs-TXJA","children":[{"id":"243","parent":"242","text":"Robusto → HbA1c <7-7.5%","guid":"WWCOmEwyS_CYTgfJtNGm4g","children":[]},{"id":"244","parent":"242","text":"Fragil/multimorbido → HbA1c <8-8.5%","guid":"c_slKcZURh-pC7ngRTA5kA","children":[]},{"id":"245","parent":"242","text":"Fin de vida → evitar hipo e hiperglicemia sintomatica","guid":"nacX8awLQXyFakytkDrzKg","children":[]}]},{"id":"246","parent":"241","text":"Deprescripcion","guid":"JvddxNTSS4GChB9obr1vpg","children":[{"id":"247","parent":"246","text":"Revisar sulfonilureas → cambiar a opciones mas seguras","guid":"Xtt_JbK6RBWf68u0rOiu6g","children":[]},{"id":"248","parent":"246","text":"Glibenclamida → NUNCA en adulto mayor","guid":"7wKdDRtcQruUBDCEWoSJjA","children":[]},{"id":"249","parent":"246","text":"iSGLT2 → riesgo CAD euglicemica + deshidratacion","guid":"MO5tcsTOTl6_tHEkC25Xyw","children":[]},{"id":"250","parent":"246","text":"Metformina → ajustar por funcion renal","guid":"SlrdGn3uSMa9XlkfpV095g","children":[]}]},{"id":"251","parent":"241","text":"Riesgo de delirium","guid":"QmmT0eOvQMSQyJpbVaYorA","children":[{"id":"252","parent":"251","text":"Tanto hipo como hiperglicemia → precipitantes de delirium","guid":"izDBN7vvSe2QEr7I_HQaig","children":[]},{"id":"253","parent":"251","text":"Buscar activamente en todo AM con emergencia diabetica","guid":"C6LxQyuGRWqBuAU8D1lcOw","children":[]}]},{"id":"254","parent":"241","text":"Fragilidad y funcionalidad","guid":"tZIl0-HWRKS_QPj2H0YHMg","children":[{"id":"255","parent":"254","text":"Evaluar capacidad de automanejo","guid":"jVc093NGR76FvmBlzmZukQ","children":[]},{"id":"256","parent":"254","text":"Considerar soporte familiar/cuidador","guid":"4iOrcBVZS5WtLqHW2syxxw","children":[]},{"id":"257","parent":"254","text":"Simplificar esquema insulinico al alta","guid":"2vmBifMmTdKGcQKssl-gmg","children":[]}]},{"id":"258","parent":"241","text":"Nutricion","guid":"wIqCZZHnRrGekiiA3JZoDA","children":[{"id":"259","parent":"258","text":"Sarcopenia + desnutricion → menor reserva","guid":"OjyV7HMbTLeDAYLXq_5KWA","children":[]},{"id":"260","parent":"258","text":"Valoracion nutricional post evento","guid":"W6OoURIjQOqcRElOaCieIA","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"261","parent":"0","text":"LR DIAGNOSTICOS","guid":"pfF8qHHcTJa0oTZF0su_OA","children":[{"id":"262","parent":"261","text":"CRITERIOS BIOQUIMICOS (ADA 2009)","guid":"R_VAyoSIRlul7Ps6Gol8VA","children":[{"id":"263","parent":"262","text":"DKA -> Glucosa >250 + cetonas + pH <7.30 + HCO3 <18 + anion gap >12 -> PMID:19564476","guid":"wTmwKoXgT0iK7d11JGgQEQ","children":[]},{"id":"264","parent":"262","text":"DKA leve -> pH 7.25-7.30 / HCO3 15-18","guid":"OvDzt4tlRjmfLrwtXHtnIA","children":[]},{"id":"265","parent":"262","text":"DKA moderada -> pH 7.00-7.24 / HCO3 10-15","guid":"OagkJgXORDe4M6Ev3Opq5Q","children":[]},{"id":"266","parent":"262","text":"DKA severa -> pH <7.00 / HCO3 <10","guid":"Gr3wBYYHSyGZ7NWsGLyTOQ","children":[]},{"id":"267","parent":"262","text":"EHH -> Glucosa >600 + Osm efectiva >320 + pH >7.30 + HCO3 >18 + sin cetonas significativas -> PMID:19564476","guid":"cRSRyo_nQkC0GuoZvDxGew","children":[]}]},{"id":"268","parent":"261","text":"HALLAZGOS CLINICOS (cabecera)","guid":"fRtBoB7fQd2nAcLgsEW7Ag","children":[{"id":"269","parent":"268","text":"Respiracion de Kussmaul -> [LR no consolidado formalmente, signo de acidosis severa]","guid":"kBNYrsQzTqCSul4xVsbe9g","children":[]},{"id":"270","parent":"268","text":"Aliento cetonico (fruity breath) -> [LR no consolidado, especifico pero insensible]","guid":"CBaa-L76RkeCFP5YQZlerA","children":[]},{"id":"271","parent":"268","text":"Deshidratacion severa (mucosas secas, turgor) -> marcador severidad no LR especifico","guid":"J33-qyYAQ2aDBqdMj_p8GA","children":[]},{"id":"272","parent":"268","text":"Poliuria / polidipsia / polifagia -> hiperglicemia general no DKA/EHH","guid":"As4x97-oQXe9LiV1-rZEDQ","children":[]},{"id":"273","parent":"268","text":"Alteracion sensorio + Osm calculada >320 -> [definitorio EHH]","guid":"W2h1OAsqSgqNHan_L8itzw","children":[]},{"id":"274","parent":"268","text":"Dolor abdominal en DKA (hasta 40 porciento) -> frecuente pero inespecifico","guid":"JrW6UW7tTUOP4kfBouiaoA","children":[]}]},{"id":"275","parent":"261","text":"HALLAZGOS LABORATORIO","guid":"O9YodjhHQly8wJ0BJkC5Ww","children":[{"id":"276","parent":"275","text":"Cetonemia capilar beta-hidroxibutirato >=3.0 mmol/L + glicemia + pH -> [diagnostico DKA] -> PMID:18184896","guid":"2Al8T82gS4C61j9hu2I5lg","children":[]},{"id":"277","parent":"275","text":"Cetonuria 3+ en DKA -> apoya dx","guid":"6xQ9rCaFRQ66DjLZfuTv0Q","children":[]},{"id":"278","parent":"275","text":"Brecha anionica >12 mEq/L -> acidosis metabolica con AG aumentado","guid":"aPvEC591QWah-GNTHjTgxA","children":[]},{"id":"279","parent":"275","text":"Hipokalemia inicial en DKA -> K total corporal DISMINUIDO aunque serico variable","guid":"WxJbMMpCR6-ig2meySKuJQ","children":[]},{"id":"280","parent":"275","text":"Osmolaridad efectiva = 2Na + glucosa/18 -> definitorio EHH si >320","guid":"oNKd6uMnQ0SNlJZaEhUlgg","children":[]}]},{"id":"281","parent":"261","text":"INTERPRETACION","guid":"tfHxMSMJTgawP48bsV0SJw","children":[{"id":"282","parent":"281","text":"DKA y EHH son DIAGNOSTICOS POR CRITERIOS BIOQUIMICOS COMPUESTOS","guid":"M5fOTtaWSOyciz6HcmlQSg","children":[]},{"id":"283","parent":"281","text":"Signos clinicos clasicos son ESPECIFICOS PERO INSENSIBLES","guid":"AO2-W5I6RT2cjLbO_jsAWQ","children":[]},{"id":"284","parent":"281","text":"LRs individuales no publicados formalmente por ese motivo","guid":"lam4ButuQWWZg64rfR77ig","children":[]}]},{"id":"285","parent":"261","text":"GERIATRIA","guid":"uG46wrzlTKiuW3w_-FHuig","children":[{"id":"286","parent":"285","text":"EHH es 10x mas frecuente que DKA en AM","guid":"K0wkXX12Sge_W_arkYscnw","children":[]},{"id":"287","parent":"285","text":"Mortalidad EHH 5-20 porciento","guid":"8zD4IDSgT1uq8-8X8Qs8aA","children":[]},{"id":"288","parent":"285","text":"Infeccion como precipitante en mayoria de casos","guid":"RV56aq_cQ9GXrwZjcg_ucQ","children":[]},{"id":"289","parent":"285","text":"Alteracion sensorial puede ser unico signo","guid":"sbna1GgmRD-J-lQQOqNC4w","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"290","parent":"0","text":"Perlas Clinicas","guid":"raP1hqkCR9yDwerK_UeTJQ","children":[{"id":"291","parent":"290","text":"CAD euglicemica: iSGLT2 + estres → glicemia normal\\No solo levemente alta pero pH bajo y cetonas altas.","guid":"emlPR07gQb6z01Q_KOolPQ","children":[]},{"id":"292","parent":"290","text":"EHH es MAS COMUN en adulto mayor que CAD; presenta\\Naltura sensorial como unico signo en hasta 30%.","guid":"IM8enI4sRNGd3qf2GXYTag","children":[]},{"id":"293","parent":"290","text":"Infeccion es el precipitante mas comun de\\Ndescompensaciones hiperglicemicas en AM.","guid":"wcJRdzFxSv2Tcs7dXvvxLQ","children":[]},{"id":"294","parent":"290","text":"NO iniciar insulina hasta K >3.3 mEq/L\\N(arritmia letal).","guid":"DIvEx94gSrG-7Q6QCvTCEA","children":[]},{"id":"295","parent":"290","text":"Reposicion de potasio: K <5.2 → agregar 20-30 mEq/L\\Nal SF; K <3.3 → reponer ANTES de insulina.","guid":"M8_mSA79RuWomjipDQ7ogw","children":[]},{"id":"296","parent":"290","text":"Bicarbonato solo si pH <6.9 (riesgo edema cerebral\\Nen pediatria, sin beneficio en adulto).","guid":"Rzpbbu6dQmW9SKzFend3KQ","children":[]},{"id":"297","parent":"290","text":"ADA 2024: HbA1c objetivo individualizado en AM\\N7-7.5% sano, 7.5-8% comorbilidad, 8-8.5% fragil.","guid":"ClO0XvvdTWmkEYbgxflmeA","children":[]},{"id":"298","parent":"290","text":"Evitar glibenclamida y clorpropamida en >65 anos\\N(hipoglicemia prolongada Beers Criteria).","guid":"NzjS3F4dTIqIj8MBOB85Wg","children":[]},{"id":"299","parent":"290","text":"Hipoglicemia INADVERTIDA en AM: ausencia de\\Nsintomas adrenergicos por neuropatia autonomica.","guid":"dFpbUhQwS62oKArxrLywcg","children":[]},{"id":"300","parent":"290","text":"Hipoglicemia severa ↑ riesgo CV y demencia\\N(Lee 2018) - evitar a toda costa en AM.","guid":"RycYsv1EQWmzkjtP9Da2DA","children":[]},{"id":"301","parent":"290","text":"IAM tipo 2 frecuente en descompensacion diabetica:\\Ntroponina elevada por demanda no por placa rota.","guid":"4owGM8J0TXG66YJ2BK21Ag","children":[]},{"id":"302","parent":"290","text":"AM con DM tienen 2x riesgo de caidas\\N(Burgess 2023) - revisar farmacos hipoglicemiantes.","guid":"f81KpMM5Rnip8s-DbYGMsw","children":[]},{"id":"303","parent":"290","text":"REFERENCIAS","guid":"nIwpgsreQBuCfYM3ROl1zw","children":[{"id":"304","parent":"303","text":"Mustafa 2023 → guia JBDS manejo EHH (PMID:36370077, DOI:10.1111/dme.15005)","guid":"Qxu0ibJXSPONnspbx3UpNg","children":[]},{"id":"305","parent":"303","text":"Willix 2019 → presentaciones hiperglicemicas en DM2 (PMID:31129935, DOI:10.31128/AJGP-12-18-4785)","guid":"NhHeECSCT0ORhWEx8FL16Q","children":[]},{"id":"306","parent":"303","text":"Hritani 2018 → IAM tipo 2 en descompensacion diabetica (PMID:29518369, DOI:10.1016/j.amjmed.2018.02.007)","guid":"DSGZFqKlS8mWF-H0eOng8g","children":[]},{"id":"307","parent":"303","text":"Lee 2018 → hipoglicemia severa y eventos CV (PMID:29127240, DOI:10.2337/dc17-1669)","guid":"nxjICZ_0TkOZldqfkxeVMQ","children":[]},{"id":"308","parent":"303","text":"Burgess 2023 → DM y caidas en AM urgencia (PMID:37612537, DOI:10.1007/s41999-023-00848-0)","guid":"toG311IhSqClZWGQGXSlLg","children":[]},{"id":"309","parent":"303","text":"ADA Standards of Care 2024 → metas glicemicas en AM","guid":"C6VaZN4pTSC8GnCDx_I98Q","children":[]},{"id":"310","parent":"303","text":"Kitabchi 2009 → protocolo CAD/EHH (PMID:19564476)","guid":"017jcrz5SoKn2ryBl-B_Sw","children":[]}]}]}]},"node_count":310,"relations":[],"cross_references":[],"specialty":"Geriatría","folder":"Entidades clínicas/Geriatría/Cuidados-Domicilio","filename":"03-Sindromes-Geriatricos-Domicilio","id":"map_99","resolved_references":[]}